name: Unprincipled party
description:
Free yourself from the torment that binds your body.

In the streams of sound we lose ourselves, our thoughts and feelings. Our personality dissolves and only the body remains, which throws itself into a wild dance.
Dance helps us to forget about our problems, frees from the shackles of life and gives freedom. In the dance we are the true.
We do not want to be a victim of other people's opinions, we allow themselves to be themselves, we move and live freely.

I dance, my soul dances too
